description: This modern and stylish South Boston condo offers 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 beautifully designed bathrooms, a deeded parking space, and 954 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space. Built in 2013, the open-concept seamlessly flows from the sunlit living area to a sleek, gourmet kitchen, featuring quartz countertops, modern cabinetry, and gas cooking—ideal for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. Gleaming hardwood floors add warmth and elegance throughout, and the private deck provides an inviting outdoor retreat. Additional perks include central air, private laundry in the basement, along with sophisticated bathroom finishes that enhance the home’s modern appeal. Located just moments from public transportation, parks, top-rated restaurants, and shopping, this home offers the best of city living. Don’t miss this incredible opportunity to own in one of South Boston’s most vibrant neighborhoods!
